1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:02,876
Here is one useful thing to watch for.

2
00:00:02,826 --> 00:00:05,054
The X closes the window.

3
00:00:05,054 --> 00:00:07,540
The minus only tucks it away.

4
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:10,132
Look carefully before you click.

5
00:00:10,132 --> 00:00:14,755
If it happens, pause, reset, and try again calmly.

